Package com.room4me.xml

Interface Summary
NodeFilter This interface is an enumeration for each of the Node types.
 

Class Summary
Attribute This class represents a simple XML node attribute and allows the value to be changed.
CDATANode This class represents a CDATA section.
CommentNode This class represents an XML comment entry.
DocumentTypeNode This class represents a document type declaration in an XML document.
NakedTextNode This class represents text that is not exclusively contained by a single tag.
Node This class represents a simple XML node.
ProcessingInstructionNode This class represents a processing instruction in an XML document.
SmallXMLParser An XML document is parsed into an object model at construction time through the constructor of SmallXMLParser.
TagNode This class represents a simple XML tag (also known as an "element") node.
 

Exception Summary
MalformedXMLException This exception is thrown when a problem is detected in the XML document.
